termination_clause.text: Termination. (a) The initial term of this Agreement shall be one (1) year from the Effective Date (the "Initial Term"). This Agreementwill automatically renew for additional 1-year terms unless earlier terminated pursuant to this Agreement's express provisions (together with theInitial Term, such additional periods the "Term"). Neither Party may terminate this Agreement during the Initial Term except as set forth inparagraph 4(b) or any Exhibit. Either Party may terminate this Agreement for any reason following the Initial Term upon ninety (90) days writtennotice to the other Party.
